                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-1405" type="surname" value="PITTOCK"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-1405" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>ANN PITTOCK</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Amelia-place, Walworth-road. On the even<lb></lb>ing of Good Friday the prisoner came to my shop, and asked for two penny buns—I gave them to her—she laid down a bad shilling—I took it up and said it was very bad—she said she knew where she took it, she would take it back and get it changed—she left the shop, and I spoke to Mr. Brown, my nephew, who was having his tea—I am sure the prisoner is the woman.</p>
               <p>
