                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-1406" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY BROWN</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in the parlour. I followed the prisoner—she crossed over to Mr. Spooner's, passed the shop, and joined a young man, and went about a hundred yards down—she left him, and came back, then went to Mr. Spooner's shop, and asked for two penny buns—she took the shilling from her glove, and offered it to the servant—I went into the shop and never lost sight of her.</p>
               <p>
